"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3663"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%86%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become apparent","examples":[{"text":"Surely, the right has become apparent from the wrong."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to verify, to investigate, to seek to ascertain","examples":[{"text":"يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا إِنْ جَاءَكُمْ فَاسِقٌ بِنَبَإٍ فَتَبَيَّنُوا أَن تُصِيبُوا قَوْمًا بِجَهَالَةٍ فَتُصْبِحُوا عَلَى مَا فَعَلْتُمْ نَادِمِينَ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come to know about, to learn about, to find out","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"فَلَمَّا خَرَّ تَبَيَّنَتِ الْجِنُّ أَنْ لَوْ كَانُوا يَعْلَمُونَ الْغَيْبَ مَا لَبِثُوا فِي الْعَذَابِ الْمُهِينِ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3663","headword_ar":"تبيّن","root":"byn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", intrans.: see 1, in two places.       -A2-  As a trans. verb: see 2, in seven places. ―         -b2-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":287},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amora","text_ar":"الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought leisurely"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repeatedly, to obtain knowledge"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until he knew"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he examined, scrutinized,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"investigated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xlix. 6:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavoured, to make the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, manifest, and to settle it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"establish it, and was not hasty therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Idem in iv. 96:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proceeded, deliberately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leisurely, in the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case; not hastily:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, TA:) or it has a signification like this: in the Kur ch. iv. v. 96 and ch. xlix. v. 6, some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatabay~anuwA","text_ar":"فَتَبَيَّنُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and others"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatavab~atuwA","text_ar":"فَتَثَبَّتُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the meanings are nearly the same:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~abay~unu","text_ar":"التَّبَيُّنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"was said by Mohammad to be from God, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEajalapN","text_ar":"العَجَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. \"haste\"] from the devil. (T.)"}],"source_refs":["Ks","TA"]}]}}